WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.260 --> 00:00:04.200
Hi my name is Ben Mangrum and I'm the pastor
of a new church plant in Hamilton called

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.939
Inspiring Hope Church.

00:00:06.939 --> 00:00:12.350
We exist to inspire hope by helping people
discover God's purpose for the life, through

00:00:12.350 --> 00:00:14.600
a relationship with Jesus.

00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:21.060
Our focus is to inspire people to follow Jesus,
live in community and serve those around them

00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:24.150
in order to see God's kingdom expanded.

00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:29.779
Our church is excited to be a part of Hamilton,
and its rich history, and its community focus.

00:00:29.779 --> 00:00:33.960
One of our church's key values is to 
"Live Local".

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:40.350
And what that means is that we want to invest,
serve, and love those, in our neighborhoods,

00:00:40.350 --> 00:00:43.610
our local businesses and surrounding areas.

00:00:43.610 --> 00:00:47.200
We know the right now we are living in the
midst of an unprecedented time;

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:51.240
in our city, in our nation, and around the world.

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:56.450
And we believe that as we inspire hope to
those around us that we can make a difference.

00:00:56.450 --> 00:01:00.820
And we've started having "inspire groups" in
our home where we have a core group of people

00:01:00.820 --> 00:01:06.470
where we invest in them and inspire them to
go reach their community their neighborhood

00:01:06.470 --> 00:01:08.670
and their city with the gospel.

00:01:08.670 --> 00:01:11.900
We're going to continue to add people to our
team over these next several months,

00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:16.630
and in 2021 we're going to plant Inspiring Hope Church
here in Hamilton.

00:01:16.630 --> 00:01:22.030
To connect with us or learn more about
Inspiring Hope Church, you can shoot me an email at

00:01:22.030 --> 00:01:29.229
Ben at InspiringHopeChurch.com, or you can
connect with us at facebook.com/inspiringhopechurch

00:01:29.229 --> 00:01:30.179
We hope to hear from you soon.

